snippet.title: College Kings Act II: Part 3 [Coming May 21st to Patreon]
snippet.description:
We are extremely excited to announce the final part of Act II, coming May 21st to ALL Junior $10 Patrons and above.

Become a CK Patron today and gain access to Act II Final EP and all future versions: https://www.patreon.com/collegekings

More info: www.collegekingsgame.com
